This revision is a functioning app that utilizes basic IDE to take input from user such as variable to calculate: pressure, temperature, number of moles, or volume

The user must first choose if they're calculating a single value or creating a graph based on a range of values
	-graphing functionality unavailable

The app then collects input from user for the other variables in the ideal gas law to calculate the variable the user is looking for

The app handles some edge cases such as dividing by zero
